[68.863896, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K"]
[68.863943, "o", "           fields (\u001b[1mverbose\u001b[22m, \u001b[1mexport\u001b[22m, \u001b[1mjson\u001b[22m, \u001b[1mjson-pretty\u001b[22m, \u001b[1mjson-sse \u001b[22mand \u001b[1mjson-seq\u001b[22m), as well as\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page journalctl(1) line 328 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
[68.901315, "o", "\r\u001b[K \u001b[KESC\b\b\bESC\u001b[KO\bO\u001b[KB\bB\r\u001b[K           on \u001b[1mcat\u001b[22m. For the former, the \"__CURSOR\", \"__REALTIME_TIMESTAMP\",\u001b[m\r\n\u001b[7m Manual page journalctl(1) line 329 (press h for help or q to quit)\u001b[27m\u001b[K"]
